Author: HereToFeck
Text: I usually drink fruit juices, those boxed drinks you can get at any store and sometimes Monsters or other type of energy drinks like Hell. I didn't thought about protein shakes before. I don't like soups either for some reason, even if it's liquid i still consider it as "real food" and i just can't eat it without purging..

Author: sorrowfulspookyghost
Text: I relate actually. I hate my reflection at every weight and hate my face at every weight and can never really eat w/o purging. My only safe foods are liquids. What type of liquids do you like? Monsters and protein shakes are always super safe for me. Soup isnt for ne cause the sodium scares me
